25|$|Polarization is an {{important}} parameter in areas of science dealing with <b>transverse</b> <b>waves,</b> such as optics, seismology, radio, and microwaves. Especially impacted are technologies such as lasers, wireless and optical fiber telecommunications, and radar.|$|E
